column22: Genome-wide CRISPR gRNA screens with Mouse v2 library 2
column42: PCR products were generated using genome-wide CRISPR libraries as template DNA. Subsequently%2C PCR products are pooled and subjected to Illumina library preparation.  The library will be sequenced by HiSeq2500 RapidRun. %0A%0AThis data is part of a pre-publication release.
